Name: Marsh Worlds
Details: The Marsh Worlds are located in the Free Worlds League' anti-spinward border with the Periphery. The region contains several minor states founded after the fall of the Star League, such as the Marian Hegemony, the Lothian League, the Illyrian Palatine and the Circinius Federation, as well as independent systems like Niops and Astrokazky.
